datasets.ETTh1: An hourly-sampled electricity transformer dataset intended for electrical asset monitoring, collected from one area in a province in China.
datasets.ETTh2: An hourly-sampled electricity transformer dataset intended for electrical asset monitoring, collected from one area in a province in China.
datasets.ETTm1: A minutely-sampled electricity transformer dataset intended for electrical asset monitoring, collected from one area in a province in China.
datasets.ETTm2: A minutely-sampled electricity transformer dataset intended for electrical asset monitoring, collected from one area in a province in China.
datasets.Weather: Meteorological indicator data with ten minute sample rate.
datasets.Electricity: Hourly electricity consumption of 321 customers from 2012 to 2014.
datasets.Exchange: Daily exchange rates of the US dollar to eight different currencies ranging from 1990 to 2016.
datasets.Illness: Weekly influenza-like illness (ILI) patient data from US Centers for Disease Control (2002-2021) showing ILI patient ratio.
datasets.Traffic: Hourly road occupancy rates data from 862 detectors across the freeways of the San Francisco Bay area, covering the years 2015 to 2016.
